00:13:18.045 --> 00:13:21.150
just the amount of investment
in terms of the number of people

00:13:21.150 --> 00:13:22.859
that are working on
some of these things?

00:13:22.859 --> 00:13:25.274
ANATOLY ROPOTOV: Yeah, so for
localization and translation

00:13:25.274 --> 00:13:27.490
teams and in-house proofreading
and things like that,

00:13:27.490 --> 00:13:30.670
it's in tens of people in house.

00:13:30.670 --> 00:13:35.240
For markets like Asia, we
