about Indonesia.

00:35:01.418 --> 00:35:03.550
We see a lot in Turkey.

00:35:03.550 --> 00:35:07.170
Brazil is quite
well-known as well.

00:35:07.170 --> 00:35:09.090
The Middle East.

00:35:09.090 --> 00:35:15.030
I think Saudi Arabia,
UAE, Kuwait, Bahrain,

00:35:15.030 --> 00:35:16.910
those countries,
traditionally a lot of you

00:35:16.910 --> 00:35:20.360
probably will have very
high-spending users there.

00:35:20.360 --> 00:35:23.560
But we've never really
culturalized in those regions.

00:35:23.560 --> 00:35:27.440
We've never really created games
that cater to that audience

00:35:27.440 --> 00:35:29.731
and really support
those audiences.

00:35:29.731 --> 00:35:31.980
One of the things, people
talk about seasonal updates,

00:35:31.980 --> 00:35:34.612
like Valentine's Day not
meaning anything in Korea.

00:35:34.612 --> 00:35:36.070
One of the things
that we did is we

00:35:36.070 --> 00:35:38.254
supported Pakistan
Independence Day.

00:35:38.254 --> 00:35:40.670
And I'm not saying that because
my heritage is from there,

00:35:40.670 --> 00:35:43.950
but we did that because we
have a big audience there.

00:35:43.950 --> 00:35:45.960
And it really engaged
the community.

