AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE].

00:35:47.786 --> 00:35:48.660
SAAD CHOUDRI: No, no.

00:35:48.660 --> 00:35:51.210
Community support We
had people out there,

00:35:51.210 --> 00:35:52.450
and not just the flag.

00:35:52.450 --> 00:35:53.471
We did other things.

00:35:53.471 --> 00:35:53.970
Did--

00:35:53.970 --> 00:35:54.390
AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE].

00:35:54.390 --> 00:35:54.863
SAAD CHOUDRI: Well,
