00:35:54.863 --> 00:35:56.440
going to do that as well, right?

00:35:56.440 --> 00:35:59.119
But it's an easy win.

00:35:59.119 --> 00:36:01.160
But that's what we have
to do in emerging markets

00:36:01.160 --> 00:36:03.420
where you're not really going
to see a financial return.

00:36:03.420 --> 00:36:05.220
But you know that actually
it's going to be a burgeoning

00:36:05.220 --> 00:36:06.850
community, and they stay there.

00:36:06.850 --> 00:36:09.590
And they push the game for
you, and they help you,

00:36:09.590 --> 00:36:11.620
and you get power
users from there.

00:36:11.620 --> 00:36:14.880
So everybody's probably going
to roll out a beta program soon.

00:36:14.880 --> 00:36:18.540
People in these communities
or in other locations

00:36:18.540 --> 00:36:20.280
provide very valuable feedback.

00:36:20.280 --> 00:36:21.920
And there's a great
talent pool to see.

00:36:21.920 --> 00:36:24.720
So I think Middle
East, Africa-- we're

00:36:24.720 --> 00:36:27.560
seeing quite a bit in Nigeria--
and then Vietnam, as well,

00:36:27.560 --> 00:36:30.247
is coming up for us as well.

00:36:30.247 --> 00:36:32.080
JOE RAEBURN: So just
one really quick thing.

00:36:32.080 --> 00:36:35.380
