00:36:46.940 --> 00:36:50.790
high-spending ethnically
Chinese-living-in-America

00:36:50.790 --> 00:36:53.030
gamers coming
together to say, look,

00:36:53.030 --> 00:36:54.890
these are the alliances
that we represent.

00:36:54.890 --> 00:36:57.980
And we're all going to quit
the game until and unless you

00:36:57.980 --> 00:36:59.650
remove the Hong Kong flag.

00:36:59.650 --> 00:37:01.340
There's just grief all the time.

00:37:01.340 --> 00:37:03.500
So unless you want to
maintain every single flag

00:37:03.500 --> 00:37:06.380
for every single nation and
have selective hiding of flags--

00:37:06.380 --> 00:37:08.005
like you should
probably hide the Tibet

00:37:08.005 --> 00:37:11.924
one for Chinese audiences
as well-- just avoid

00:37:11.924 --> 00:37:12.590
a world of pain.

00:37:12.590 --> 00:37:13.726
You think they're
such a nice thing that

00:37:13.726 --> 00:37:14.809
will make everybody happy.

00:37:14.809 --> 00:37:15.430
They won't.

00:37:15.430 --> 00:37:17.660
Indonesia as well is
