office, knocked,

00:37:32.635 --> 00:37:34.760
and he said he wouldn't
leave until we offered them

00:37:34.760 --> 00:37:35.420
a special deal.

00:37:35.420 --> 00:37:36.897
So they're pretty hard-core.

00:37:36.897 --> 00:37:38.480
They're really great
gamers, and we're

00:37:38.480 --> 00:37:40.854
going to be localizing our
next game into Indonesia, too.

