increments and steps out there

00:39:18.730 --> 00:39:20.580
and figure out
how to incentivize

00:39:20.580 --> 00:39:23.960
those players to use
new payment methods,

00:39:23.960 --> 00:39:27.110
try them, using wire, SMS,
direct billing, and things

00:39:27.110 --> 00:39:27.610
like that.

00:39:27.610 --> 00:39:30.570
So it's the next big
challenge for those countries,

00:39:30.570 --> 00:39:32.790
for game developers to
really pay attention

00:39:32.790 --> 00:39:35.500
